      <h2>Format Rules</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Damage spells:</strong> Can't deal more damage than their mana cost.</li>
        <li><strong>Kill spells:</strong> Must cost 5+ mana if unconditional.</li>
        <li><strong>Counterspells:</strong> Must cost 4+ mana if unconditional.</li>
        <li><strong>Competitive cards:</strong> All staples are banned.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>
